description: Input a list of urls and the name of a custom_list that contains safe domains. Output urls where the domain is NOT present in the custom_list.

inputs.description: Supports any URL format, including FTP, HTTP, HTTPS, SMB.
inputs.name: url

inputs.description: The name of a custom list that will be used as the list of domains to filter the URL against. Only the first column of the custom list will be used. Example: https://web.example.com/ will be parsed as web.example.com and matched to values inside my_custom_list.
inputs.name: domain_allowlist

outputs.description: Only URLs that are not hosted at domains on the allow list will be returned as output.\
